edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.type

  • Packages that use edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.type 
    Package Description
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.model.system
    Contains POJOs with Hibernate 4 annotations to represent entities in the DiscourseDB System Layer
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.service.macro
    Contains service-layer classes that provide a higher level of abstraction for the DiscourseDB macro repositories defined in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.macro.
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.service.system
    Contains service-layer classes that provide a higher level of abstraction for the DiscourseDB system repositories defined in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.system.
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.service.user
    Contains service-layer classes that provide a higher level of abstraction for the DiscourseDB user repositories defined in edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.repository.user.
    edu.cmu.cs.lti.discoursedb.core.type
    This package holds enums for recurring types used in DiscourseDB.
